text: Hannes Kärkkäinen (17 July 1902 - 21 April 1938) was a Finnish diver. He competed in the men's 10 metre platform event at the 1924 Summer Olympics. ==References== Category:1902 births Category:1938 deaths Category:Finnish male divers Category:Olympic divers of Finland Category:Divers at the 1924 Summer Olympics Category:People from Lappeenranta
